Description.Text: A good, value for money hotel with easy transport links to Moscow centre. 12/08 SC
The hotel is located in a quiet residential area north of Moscow's centre, within walking distance of Petrovsko-Razumovskaya metro station.
The rooms are medium-sized and all are simply but tastefully decorated. Bathrooms with either bath or shower are in a very good condition.
A traditional facade, in keeping with the buildings around the hotel.
The restaurant is open for breakfast in the morning and serves Russian specialities during the day.
The lobby is small and looks very modern. It has a small seating area, reception desk and a bureau de change opposite.
